{
  "texts": [
    "If no viable alternative exists, and the potential risk is deemed unacceptable, regulations or societal prohibitions on the AI system's use may be necessary until a safer design is developed.",
    "Product liability should encourage producers to invest in better safety management and better instruments to improve the safety of AI product design.",
    "74 At the same time, it should encourage safe use by AI operators.",
    "The concept of misuse takes on a new dimension in the context of (semi-) autonomous systems.",
    "Courts will have to determine if AI systems adequately prevent foreseeable misuse through their design of human-machine interaction."
  ]
}